---
layout: main.njk
title: 'Maxim Van de Wynckel'
---

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-2">
    <img src="/images/profile/maxim2.jpg" alt="Maxim Van de Wynckel" class="img-fluid rounded-circle">
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-5 typography">
    <blockquote class="styled-blockquote">
    <style>
      .styled-blockquote {
        position: relative;
        padding: 1em 1.5em;
        margin: 0;
        font-style: italic;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-left: 10px solid #ccc;
      }
      .styled-blockquote:before,
      .styled-blockquote:after {
        font-size: 4em;
        position: absolute;
        color: #ccc;
      }
      .styled-blockquote:before {
        top: -0.5em;
        left: -0.8em;
      }
      .styled-blockquote:after {
        bottom: -0.5em;
        right: -0.5em;
      }
    </style>
    {% markdown %}
      Hello! My name is Maxim Van de Wynckel, a researcher at the Vrije Universiteit Brussel. I am a PhD candidate focusing on hybrid and indoor positioning, interoperability, linked data, and methods for discovering services. Read more [about me here](/about). 
      For a list of all my [academic publications, click here](/publications). I often write about my research or other projects
      in my [blog](/posts).
    {% endmarkdown %}
    </blockquote>
  </div>
  <div class="col-sm-5">

  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-3">
    <div class="col-sm-6 typography">
      <h1>Recent blog posts</h1>
      <a href="/posts">Read all posts ...</a>
      <ol reversed class="postlist">
      {% for post in collections.posts | reverse | head(3) %}
        <li class="postlist-item{% if post.url == url %} postlist-item-active{% endif %}">
          <img class="postlist-image" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}"/>
          <div class="postlist-content">
            <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="postlist-link">{% if post.data.title %}{{ post.data.title }}{% else %}<code>{{ post.url }}</code>{% endif %}</a>
            <time class="postlist-date" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            <span class="postlist-description">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
      <h1>Recent publications</h1>
      <a href="/publications">Read all publications ...</a>
      <ol reversed class="postlist">
      {% for post in collections.publications | reverse | head(3) %}
        <li class="postlist-item{% if post.url == url %} postlist-item-active{% endif %}" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ScholarlyArticle" data-type="{{ post.data.type }}">
          <img class="postlist-image" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" src="{{ post.data.thumbnail }}" itemprop="image"/>
          <div class="postlist-content">
            <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="postlist-link" itemprop="url">{% if post.data.title %}{{ post.data.title }}{% else %}<code>{{ post.url }}</code>{% endif %}</a>
            <time class="postlist-date" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}" itemprop="datePublished">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            <span class="postlist-description" itemprop="description">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</span>
          </div>
        </li>
      {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    </div>
</div>